rows.label: qst001402_msg0002
rows.name:
Oho, capable Driver really in class
of own when comes to speediness!

rows.label: qst001402_msg0003
rows.name:
Time is money!
That mean speed is more money!

rows.label: qst001402_msg0004
rows.name:
Value of life measured by contents
of bank account, meh.

rows.label: qst001402_msg0005
rows.name:
And so, having said wise saying,
Pidede depart speedily to deliver
wares to Alba Margen.

rows.label: qst001402_msg0006
rows.name:
No time for idle prattle!
Thanks, friends!
